# API Testing Collection for Postman/Thunder Client

## 1. Register User
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword123!",
  "full_name": "Demo User"
}

---

## 2. Login
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword123!"
}

# Copy the access_token from response

---

## 3. Upload Document
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/documents/upload
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

# Upload file: test_invoice.txt or any PDF/image

---

## 4. List Documents
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/documents/?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

---

## 5. Get Document Details
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/documents/{document_id}
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

---

## 6. Extract Entities (Manual)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/extraction/extract
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Policy Number: POL-123456. Coverage: $500,000. Deductible: $1,000",
  "document_type": "policy"
}
